  "body": "SHA1 is considered insecure/deprecated for use by anyone and especially for a project as important as this.\r\nPlease use SHA256 everywhere where possible.\r\n\r\nFor example look at the latest release notes with Docker images:\r\nhttps://github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/releases/tag/v2020.08.04\r\n\r\nMore info on how to use sha256 with Docker here:\r\nhttps://stackoverflow.com/questions/32046334/where-can-i-find-the-sha256-code-of-a-docker-image",
